Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.41,0:00:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我村这四百余年以来一直与世隔绝 自给自足
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至节则是一个在夏至迎回祖先灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并祈求丰收的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日天亮就开始举办 一直会持续到后天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望诸位能够过完这个节日再走不迟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们看看那边的塔楼和窗户的建筑风格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是油画里的中世纪教堂一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 你看看这板壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.09,0:00:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里还有口古井呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:00:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们干啥打枪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有狼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:00:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近的山里有野狼出没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.86,0:01:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这个村子里的人不是狼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么话 我们可是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然与山外之人确实不同种族…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.61,0:02:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎您回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么和考迪利亚长得一模一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然当时我还只是个孩子 但是我却记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曼尼娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人考迪利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老爷而言 对村子而言 都是个无法磨灭的灾星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何曼尼娅！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:37.63,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,545)}夏至节神明降旨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,案子是发生在特奥多尔老爷的书房里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚12点正 女仆会去书房伺候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候考迪利亚还只有15岁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那时让她去把水壶里的水换了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天也正好是在午夜十二点去办的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道是十二点「正」？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:04:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时有其他人在场 我们目击了她用钥匙开门进房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时我用怀表看过时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知为何 其他人的证言里时间都不统一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考迪利亚进了书房没一会儿就尖叫着跑了出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.46,0:04:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跑去一看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.45,0:04:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才发现特奥多尔老爷已经被人用短刀刺死了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知为何 地上却散了一地的金币
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金币？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 村里平常不用金币来买卖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以平常都是由特奥多尔老爷来保管的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自那晚开始 考迪利亚就高烧卧床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她退烧之后 继任村长的我就把她逐出了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐出村子？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.11,0:04:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:05:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时她随身的东西 仅剩下一个金币和一个行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等她一离开大门 我们马上收起了吊桥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.52,0:05:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个黄花大闺女 没有离开过村子一步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.36,0:05:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我们是有些担心她能不能自己过活…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.56,0:05:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人不能留在村里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会为村里招灾的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 现如今考迪利亚的女儿却回来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.58,0:05:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚到不久你就说要去散步
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.98,0:05:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们去散步吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是村长谢吉吾思的助手 叫做安布罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那啥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我只是想搞清楚 你皮肤和眼睛的颜色为何与众不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也清楚外面的人不都是金发碧眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能带我去一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您尽管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 我希望能多摸摸这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你的便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您 那么您希望去哪里看看呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.22,0:06:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考迪利亚从前的住处
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.70,0:06:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要走啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是怕被人知道带外人来这里 会惹祸上身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.94,0:07:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也没写字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是考迪利亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孩提时代的我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 考迪利亚小姐不是15岁才被赶出村子的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明曾有人来过这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人带走了之前存放在这里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且用这张成人后的考迪利亚的照片来替换了这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这片混沌有指向性吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特奥多尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是前任村长的坟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦 维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.51,0:07:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可以对坟墓做出这样不敬的举动…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我并非罪人 C」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.57,0:07:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是考迪利亚？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这肯定是考迪利亚写的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲果然是遭人冤枉而被赶出村子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 谁才是罪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.61,0:08:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.52,0:08:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久城？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是笑声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是和维多利嘉的眼睛一样的颜色…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.18,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是狼吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.81,0:08:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我放水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再玩一盘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给钱我可以考虑放水喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 电话怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们两个小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…米尔德瑞德小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这里有电话 就说明其实这里通了电吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错 村长明明说这里自给自足…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得奇怪 就问了那个有点神经兮兮的女仆…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里好像有个赞助者喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.76,0:09:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞助者？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.90,0:09:28.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫啥名来着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫啥布莱恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 是个叫布莱恩·罗斯科的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布莱恩·罗斯科…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.55,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个人似乎是离开村子的人的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.15,0:09:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说10年前他就出过资了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.82,0:09:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.00,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 打牌也打腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去教堂看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才外面有狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼来了那个讨厌的老村长会帮我们赶走的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 我们去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 衣服又皱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身打扮蕾丝花边实在太多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前布莱恩·罗斯科来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟有何目的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他应该是来村里架设电线的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前那可是世界大战刚刚打响的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那种年代里 为何还要不慌不忙地到小山村里通电线呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10年前的话 那张照片的拍摄年代就说得通了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是洗澡水 请掺冷水慢慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能洗澡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 有事就叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:10:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我人就在这里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱洗澡皮肤好好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}原来是在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.05,0:11:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎维多利嘉也恢复常态了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.78,0:11:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉 里面没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 久城 你吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来有人想要恐吓我 来把我赶出村子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去吧 这村里一股阴森的气氛 让人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.56,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会保护我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.95,0:12:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不得了 这是红芜菁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这辆车子是冬军的车子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬军？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,广场上的男人们会扮演冬夏两军来模拟打仗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.39,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏军会把冬军的头领冬之男打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把大车点火烧掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.35,0:12:59.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.47,0:13:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是想侮辱本村的话就请离开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无聊啊 都这个时代了还讲迷信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子也太那啥了 你说是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这样 要是现在被赶出村子的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那个…这家伙就是嘴上没口德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.83,0:13:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回房去吧 好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.02,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那群人昨晚就在教堂里胡闹来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当着村里人的面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把装饰在墙上的酒壶扔进了圣水盆里 好大的动静呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醉鬼哪里还会讲道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.57,0:13:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在那里嗤笑说为啥要看重这种破烂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.94,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明自己才是最看重古董的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:57.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给 给你拿了些节日点心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是亚兰先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然嘴上那样说 他也是喜欢热闹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道这个是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是安布罗斯先生吗？挺帅气的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬之男 化为灰烬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸人怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿水来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亚兰先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.49,0:15:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个事故
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他想要妨碍节日 所以自己和纸人调换了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这客人真是傻得可以
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:15:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.79,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢吉吾思村长 这是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当姑娘们扔榛子的时候 这个人正经过广场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.59,0:16:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时广场上人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为他不可能和纸人调换过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过犹不及 多言伤身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.91,0:16:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至节不能因此中止
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接下来要去教堂主持仪式 就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有人死了 但是庆祝却不停下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个村子果然很奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吗 维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 维多利嘉？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会保护我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥先生 你也来这里谘询未来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当夏军胜利 丰收有了保障
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教堂就会一直空到傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为教堂是连着那个世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.15,0:17:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以来观战的祖先的灵魂也会经过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.91,0:17:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他们走之前 祖先的灵魂会借村长之口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来回答孩子们的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.23,0:17:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一弥先生 难得来一次 来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我还要找维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 安布罗斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个 我在找维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.62,0:18:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是找她 那大可不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那女孩与你不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想问些什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我就只有她一个朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后我能和维多利嘉…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不会死在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是数年之后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.48,0:18:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会掀起一股席卷世界的潮流吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个根基未稳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕会因为那阵潮流而各奔东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的心会一直连在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会分开…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也来这里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.64,0:19:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问了啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问了我会不会再长个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长啥啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.60,0:19:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身高？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这都问的啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是被说了好大一通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你生啥气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 不说一声就不知跑到哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去书房了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:11.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪人考迪利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.85,0:20:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是这样从背后刺了老爷一刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到短刀的刀柄没入…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「可老爷是个成年人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.68,0:20:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「考迪利亚才15岁 身高差得太多了」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.93,0:20:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将短刀完全插入成年人的背部 小孩子是无法够到也无法做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是她就成了罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂被打上了肮脏的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果犯人另有其人的话…你是这样想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智慧之泉已经倾诉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片完全重构之时来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说被完全重构了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.57,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你已经知道谁是犯人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 即使知道犯人 我也没有证据…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.50,0:21:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使出了人命 即使狼也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏至节也绝不能中断
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟上去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.60,0:22:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维多利嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经听不见狼的声音了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.88,0:22:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.07,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了 安布罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.46,0:22:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二个了 久城
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现世的罪煌煌泛光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去的罪被其照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.05,0:24:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么我有种很不好的预感…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.97,0:24:29.98,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,560)}故国中吠声响彻
